  "zipball_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/zipball/v2024.10.21",
  "body": "# Information\r\nThis pre-release rewrites the firmware builder and moves all chip-specific customization directly into the YAML manifests, in addition to renaming the firmware types. This is a breaking change for all firmware types. Please see the changes to [the ZBT-1 manifest](https://github.com/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/pull/82/files#diff-223023eb892776526a20ebf517a471997dfa0424ff1c817f371b8674afd3dc87) for an example of how to migrate.\r\n\r\nThis pre-release also introduces preliminary support for our XNCP custom commands. This is a work-in-progress and Zigbee software support will arrive over time. Do not rely on this command set to be stable, it will change in a future release.\r\n\r\n## What's Changed\r\n* Template projects by @puddly in https://github.com/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/pull/82\r\n* Custom XNCP protocol commands by @puddly in https://github.com/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/pull/57\r\n* Add zap tooling to Docker container by @tl-sl in https://github.com/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/pull/84\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @tl-sl made their first contribution in https://github.com/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/pull/84\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/NabuCasa/silabs-firmware-builder/compare/v2024.8.20...v2024.10.21",
  "mentions_count": 2
}
